# Chapadevs Design Pattern

IT consultancy focused on small business, with a big-company design. Modern, sharp, professional.

## UI Component Library

All reusable UI elements live in `frontend/src/components/ui-components/`. Always import from the barrel export:

```jsx
import { Button, Card, Input, Select, Textarea, Badge, PageTitle, SectionTitle, Container, Alert, Tag } from '../../components/ui-components'
```

**Never create one-off button, card, input, badge, or alert styles in component CSS.** Use the standardized components below.

---

## Component Reference

### Button

```jsx
<Button variant="primary" size="md" to="/path" onClick={fn} disabled={bool}>Text</Button>
```

| Prop | Values | Default |
|------|--------|---------|
| `variant` | `primary`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `danger` | `primary` |
| `size` | `xs`, `sm`, `md`, `lg`, `hero` | `md` |
| `to` | Route path (renders as Link) | — |
| `href` | External URL (renders as anchor) | — |
| `as` | Custom element tag | `button` |

### Card

```jsx
<Card variant="accent" className="p-6">{children}</Card>
```

| Variant | Usage |
|---------|-------|
| `default` | General purpose card with border + shadow |
| `elevated` | Higher shadow for emphasis |
| `accent` | Green bottom border (dashboard blocks) |
| `ghost` | Gray background, subtle |
| `outline` | Green-tinted border (auth cards) |

### Input / Select / Textarea

```jsx
<Input id="email" label="Email" required error="Invalid email" placeholder="you@example.com" />
<Select id="role" label="Role" required>{options}</Select>
<Textarea id="desc" label="Description" rows={3} />
```

All form components support: `label`, `error`, `required`, `id`, `className`, `wrapperClassName`, and forward refs.

### Badge

```jsx
<Badge variant="development">In Progress</Badge>
```

| Category | Variants |
|----------|----------|
| Semantic | `success`, `warning`, `error`, `neutral`, `info` |
| Status | `holding`, `open`, `ready`, `development`, `completed`, `cancelled`, `default` |
| Role | `admin`, `client`, `programmer`, `user` |

### PageTitle / SectionTitle

```jsx
<PageTitle>Dashboard</PageTitle>
<SectionTitle className="mb-4">Project Details</SectionTitle>
```

- `PageTitle` → h1 with green left border, Code Bold, uppercase
- `SectionTitle` → h3 with green left border, Code Bold, uppercase (accepts `as` prop for different tag)

### Container

```jsx
<Container>{children}</Container>
```

Max-width 1200px, centered, with horizontal padding.

### Alert

```jsx
<Alert variant="error">{message}</Alert>
```

| Variant | Usage |
|---------|-------|
| `error` | Red — validation errors, API failures |
| `success` | Green — confirmations |
| `info` | Blue — informational messages |
| `warning` | Amber — warnings |

Returns `null` if no children (safe to render conditionally).

### Tag

```jsx
<Tag variant="skill">React</Tag>
```

| Variant | Usage |
|---------|-------|
| `default` | Gray background, neutral |
| `primary` | Green tint, service/feature tags |
| `skill` | Green tint, skill/tech tags |
| `outline` | Border only, no fill |

