## Color Palette

Defined in `tailwind.config.js` and CSS variables in `styles.css`.

| Role | Tailwind Class | CSS Variable | Hex |
|------|---------------|-------------|-----|
| Primary | `bg-primary`, `text-primary` | `--primary-green` | #059669 |
| Primary Dark | `bg-primary-dark` | `--primary-green-dark` | #047857 |
| Primary Light | `bg-primary-light` | `--primary-green-light` | #10b981 |
| Text Main | `text-ink` | `--text-primary` | #111827 |
| Text Secondary | `text-ink-secondary` | `--text-secondary` | #374151 |
| Text Muted | `text-ink-muted` | `--text-light` | #6b7280 |
| Surface | `bg-surface` | `--background` | #ffffff |
| Surface Gray | `bg-surface-gray` | `--background-gray` | #f9fafb |
| Surface Green | `bg-surface-green` | `--background-light-green` | #ecfdf5 |
| Border | `border-border` | `--border` | #e5e7eb |

**Avoid**: Neon greens (#00ff87), blue accents, purple, or colors outside this palette.

## Typography

Defined in `tailwind.config.js`:

| Role | Tailwind Class | Font Family |
|------|---------------|-------------|
| Headings | `font-heading` | Code Bold, monospace |
| Buttons/Nav | `font-button` | Creato Display Medium, serif |
| Body | `font-body` | Coolvetica, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif |

## Sharp Modern Look

- `border-radius: 0` on everything — Tailwind config sets `rounded` default to `0`
- Clean lines, minimal decoration
- Shadows: `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, `shadow-lg`, `shadow-xl`

## Layout

- **Max content width**: `max-w-[1200px]` or `<Container>`
- **Container padding**: `px-8`

## Quick Checks

- [ ] Using UI components (`Button`, `Card`, `Input`, etc.) instead of raw `<button>`, `<div>` with one-off styles
- [ ] No `border-radius` on buttons/cards (enforced by Tailwind config)
- [ ] Font families match: `font-heading` / `font-button` / `font-body`
- [ ] No neon or off-palette greens (#00ff87, etc.)
- [ ] Page titles use `<PageTitle>` component
- [ ] Section titles use `<SectionTitle>` component
- [ ] Error/success messages use `<Alert>` component
- [ ] Status badges use `<Badge>` with status variant
- [ ] Tags/chips use `<Tag>` component
- [ ] Import from `components/ui-components` barrel export, not individual files
